
This course shows you how to:
• Install and set up OneDrive on Windows, Mac, iOS and Android
• Sync, backup, and organize your files and folders
• Securely share files and collaborate with others in real time
• Use OneDrive’s Personal Vault for protecting sensitive documents
• Search your files and photos with powerful AI tools
• Creating and edit M365 files right from OneDrive
• Manage storage space and keep files offline when you need them
